title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Nov 23 2021
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Nov 23 2021
description:
Kyle Rittenhouse speaks out in first interview and has a direct message for Biden. Crime in major cities skyrockets - welcome to "Lib Dystopia." Clay and Buck vow to continue Rush's Thanksgiving tradition while also making some new ones.  Will Cain on the Democrats branding issue and CNN's transition from bias to propagandist to activist.
